{
  "stem": "27770.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They just came out with a law that, for this age up to this age, every Jewish man has to appear, city hall, register himself.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't care if that guy had a family, how this guy will live, how the family will survive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With my father, it was a [? lock, ?] because when they, each year, as he was in the forced labor, in 1944, they wanted to take him also to send him to Russia.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had trouble with his kidneys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- when they send him the letter to be-- go to the army, again, to the forced labor, he had a connection in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took him in, in a hospital, with a little connection, with a certain doctor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They called it [HUNGARIAN] Sanatorium.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was there about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when came the paper, he should go to the army, the doctor said, he has to operated.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He will stay here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, he was there two weeks in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the doctor said, Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Schlesinger, we will do everything for you, what we can.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there, you have to make up your mind, or you going to have the operation, or we have to send you out, and you have to go to the army, to the forced labor?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the Munkatsh rebbe, who was very famous, a Munkatsh rebbe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had a son-in-law, who came from Poland, a well-educated man, who is still today in Israel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He used to be the chief rabbi in South America, in Brazil.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And later on, he became, in Lehavot, also a chief rabbi.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
